{What is this doing here in the RKCB Practice Pages?

To emphasize that there are many 4NT bids which are NOT asking for Aces.

In this case, SOUTH showed a balanced hand with 18 or 19 points, and NORTH invited him 
to bid 6NT if he felt his hand was a "maximum". He didn't, so he passed.}

